title: ISic000778. I.Sicily inscription 000778
body:
Facsimile Images

L(ucia) Arria Parteenin
vixit annos XXVI
Parthenius pat<e>r
filiae dulcissimae
5fecit

Apparatus criticus

Text of Libertini

translation

commentary

Solin (Arctos 21 (1987), 137-138) observes that the name Parteenin is probably a variant on the orthographically correct form Partheni(o)n
